  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Circle2D
    Circle2D implements a basic circle class with useful operations regularly used in path generation.
    Geometry
    A utility class encompassing various useful geometry algorithms.
    Line2D
    Represents a line in the form r = r0 +td Where r is the line, r0 is an arbitrary point on the line, t is a constant and d is a directional unit vector.
